data.name: HCS Kickoff Major Charlotte 2023
data.description:
Welcome back Spartans! Join us in Charlotte, NC as we kickoff the first Major of the 2023 HCS season.

With fresh rosters, new storylines, and heated rivalries, the stage is set for this to be an intense year of Halo Esports. Will OpTic Gaming keep their crown and defend their title or will there be a new champion? Year 2 of HCS starts now!

tournaments.name: HCS Kickoff Major Charlotte 2023 FFA
tournaments.description: HCS Kickoff Major Charlotte 2023 features a free Halo FFA tournament! The event will be open for up to 512 players. Best of luck to those competing for their shot at the largest piece of the $5,000 prize pool!

tournaments.name: HCS Kickoff Major Charlotte 2023 4v4
tournaments.description: The best Halo Infinite teams from around the world will be competing at the HCS Kickoff Major Charlotte 2023 for their chance to claim the top reward from the $250,000 prize pool! Be sure to secure your team pass and prepare for an epic tournament.
